      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>A <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">panel</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.46</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.34</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.13</measure>) with worn edges; only the right side survives intact. A groove has been cut in the back.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>Cut on the face.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>lunate, irregular, but carefully cut, av. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p>Probably <date exact="none" cert="low" notBefore="0401" notAfter="0600">fifth/sixth century</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
		<ab>
		<lb n="1"/><g type="cross"/> <w lemma="ἐνθάδε">ἐνθάδε</w> <w lemma="κατάκειμαι"><orig reg="κατάκειται">κα
		<lb n="2" type="worddiv"/>τάκιτε</orig></w> <persName key="epiphanios1" reg="Ἐπιφάνιος" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Ἐπιφάνιος">Ἐπι
		<lb n="3" type="worddiv"/>φάνις</name></persName> <rs type="profession" key="taurotrophos"><w lemma="ταυρωτρόφος">ταυρ
		<lb n="4" type="worddiv"/>ωτρόφος</w></rs>
		</ab>
	  </div>

	  <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>Here lies Epiphani<supplied reason="omitted">o</supplied>s, bull-rearer</ab>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="IX.40">IX.40</xref>, and for the phrasing, <xref type="eAla-text" n="IX.39">IX.39</xref>.</p>
      </div>

